[{"Id": 1012880, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Anas is reported to have quoted the Holy Prophet (s) as saying: Whoever says this supplicatory prayer every morning and every evening, Allah the All-exalted will order four angels to defend him from the front side, the backside, the right side, and the left side, he will be kept under the security of Allah the Almighty and All-majestic, and no harm can ever affect him even if all jinn and all human beings try to cause him harm…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Anas se riwaayat hai, us ne kaha keh Hazrat Rasool-e-Khuda (s) ne farmaya keh jo shakhs Subh o Shaam yeh dua padhe to Haq Taala chaar (4) farishte bhejega jo uske aage-peechhe aur daaye-baaye se uski hifaazat karenge aur woh Khuda ki amaan mein hoga. Agar Jinn o Ins usey nuqsaan pohonchaane ki sar-tod koshish kare to bhi usey nuqsaan nahi pohoncha sakenge…", "UrduDescription": " انس سے روایت ہے کہ اس نے کہا: حضرت رسول اﷲ ؐ نے فرمایا : جو شخص صبح و شام یہ دعا پڑھے تو حق تعالی ٰچار فرشتے بھیجے گا جو اس کے آگے پیچھے اور دائیں بائیں سے اس کی حفاظت کریں گے اور وہ خدا کی امان میں ہو گا۔ اگر جن و انس اسے نقصان پہنچانے کی پوری کوشش کریں تو بھی اسے نقصان نہیں پہنچا سکیں گے ا ور وہ دعا یہ ہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "A